description:
Welcome to JimLiElevators: My name is Jim and I am an elevator photographer based in central Texas. I have always loved elevators when I was a kid. Been filming since 2005. I present to you videos of elevators that are both vintage and modern. Not only that I film elevators, but I've also been interested into trains as well. I'll occasionally upload animated elevators because I've had a lot of fun making them. So with that said, I hope you enjoy your visit to my channel.

Thanks so much for your loyal viewership. I take pride in keeping this channel clean for all ages. I am also a born Christian, so I want to keep it pleasing to Jesus as well! “For God so loved the world that he gave his only son that believes in him shall not perish but have eternal life. John 3:16."

I'm also thankful to Andrew Reams (DieselDucy) who's the deepest inspiration towards me to start this channel. That said, make sure you subscribe. Thanks and have a great day! :D

We love them as much as you do, but these are not backyard torture tests. 

Our testing is performed within highly controlled environments by technicians with the technology, training, and experience required to generate repeatable data. Governments and technologists rely on the veracity HP White reports to develop, certify, procure, and field the PPE that warfighters, law enforcement officers, corrections professionals, firefighters, and other truly amazing people, trust with their lives.

Subscribe to see real-time and high speed videos of testing in accordance with global PPE standards; such as, NIJ, ISO, ASTM, ANSI, HECC, BS EN, NFPA, NOCSAE, HOSDB, STANAG, and many others. You'll see ballistic and non-ballistic testing on body armor, helmets, eyewear, gloves, bomb suits, turnout gear, HazMat suits, and more.

description:
HYRobotics is one of the world's leading suppliers of robots for the injection molding industry. We have been manufacturing robots in South Korea since 1988. Currently we are manufacturing over 500 traverse robots and 1000 sprue pickers a year. We have been supplying robots to United States since 1996. Our robots were originally were marketed through a major catalog company. In 2002 the decision made was made to manufacture robots for the U.S under our own name and HYRobotics USA was founded in St. Louis, Missouri.

Olen ajanut Helsingin paikallisliikenteessä linja-autoa yli vuoden. Nyt työskentelen Kaupunkiraideliikennekuljettajana Kaupunkiliikenne Oy:llä. Videopeleissä minulla on käytössä: PS4 ja pelitietokone. Tietokoneessa käytän Steelseriesin kuulokkeita, hiirtä ja näppäimistöä. Muita: Joystick, Peliohjain, G27 ratti ja Raildriver. 

Minun tietokoneen kokoonpano/My computer specs: 
Processor: i7-10700K
Graphic card: Asus GeForce RTX 3080 TUF Gaming OC
Ram: 32GB
Operating system: Windows 10

I am man from Helsinki and I born in 1993. I usually publish videos from videogames, public transport and travelling. I drived one year local bus. Now I work for Helsinki City Transport (HKL) and I am  Urban rail transit driver. I have PS4 and computer. I use Steelseries headset, mouse and keyboard. Other: Gamepad, Joystick, G27 wheel and Raildriver.

description:
http://www.unchealthblueridge.org On October 1, 2021, we became UNC Health Blue Ridge and joined the UNC Health family. The organizations share a unique and special commitment to rural healthcare in the Mountain Region of North Carolina and are jointly committed to enhancing and growing access to high-quality healthcare close to home for generations to come. 

UNC Health Blue Ridge is a comprehensive healthcare system, providing advanced healthcare and wellness services from nearly 50 locations across a three-county region of Western North Carolina. The system includes one hospital with two locations, a wellness center, and a continuing care retirement community. description:
The Wu-Tang Clan is an American hip hop group from Staten Island, New York City, originally composed of East Coast rappers RZA, GZA, Ol' Dirty Bastard, Method Man, Raekwon, Ghostface Killah, Inspectah Deck, U-God and Masta Killa. Cappadonna later became an official member of the group. The Wu-Tang Clan has released four gold and platinum studio albums. Its 1993 debut album, Enter the Wu-Tang (36 Chambers), is considered to be one of the greatest albums in hip-hop history.

The Wu-Tang Clan has introduced and launched the careers of a number of affiliated artists and groups, often collectively known as the Wu-Tang Killa Bees, and has been described as one of the most influential hip-hop groups of all-time. In 2008, About ranked them "the No. 1 greatest hip hop group of all time". Kris Ex of Rolling Stone called Wu-Tang Clan "the best rap group ever".  In 2004, NME hailed them as one of the most influential groups of the last ten years.

LEKKERBOY DISC 2 OUT NOW

Cats out the bag. Sticky have started a label. It’s called Westway of course. Introducing Danté Knows @Dante.knows
Many may wonder why we’d launch a label. When we’ve prided ourselves off not needing one so long. This is sumn a lil different. This is a label run by musicians, for musicians.
We aint doing this for money. We wanna build artists from the bottom up - real ones we believe in. No shitty bank loan deals and nothin that could ever hinder those we care for most.  Danté is more than an artist to us. He is family. Who we wanna spend the rest of our days with.

description:
Paper Machinery Corporation is the world’s leading designer and manufacturer of advanced, cutting edge forming machines for paperboard cups, containers, and custom packages.
 
Since 1951, it has been our mission to provide the latest cutting-edge engineering, technology and innovation to the machinery manufacturing industry.  As forward thinking innovators, engineers, and highly trained technicians, we continue to set the standard for state-of-the-art forming machines that meet the complex needs of packagers worldwide for generations to come.
 
All of PMC’s products are built to last, and deliver speed, capacity, reliability and durability.  PMC’s state-of-the-art machinery includes the PMC 2001S and PMC 2500S servo drive models and high speed PMC 1003 cup forming machine. PMC’s overwrapping machines are widely used in packaging and hot drink applications. PMC also offers double wall, triple wall and specialty wrapping machines with customer specified configurations.

description:
This is my gaming video account, my normal account is also ddraig au (beats me)

(old, see update below) At the moment this is almost entirely Planetside 2 footage - as that's about the only game I play lately.  This footage is recorded originally @ 60fps / 1080p using shadowplay, and then compressed into x264 / 30fps and uploaded here. No voice comms is recorded, only what comes out of the speakers.   Since dropping the shadowplay buffer from 20 minutes to 10 minutes I seem to not have stuttering issues - interesting.

Update: 4k footage, 20 minute buffer again, I'll record voice comms, because after 10 years of not recording voices, I think that was a bad idea.  *shrug*. I'm also playing games other than Planetside 2, lately - although that is still my favourite game

Welcome to Ryan Michad's Handgun Radio Channel! Here I try to go over firearms that you may not see fired or reviewed elsewhere, along with high-speed footage of classic & modern firearms.  I really enjoy being able to showcase some of the interesting guns that I get to shoot, along with giving you a little bit of the history behind them. Many videos here are referenced in the Handgun Radio Podcast on the Firearms Radio Network! Be sure to go like the Handgun Radio Facebook Page as well!  I hope to upload a few videos a week, but with work and life, that can change depending upon events.  Please subscribe and share the videos and thank you very much for watching!!

Feel free to message me with any questions!

Also, check out our Facebook page at www.facebook.com/handgunradio for all your talk radio handgunning needs!

Visit www.firearmsradio.tv for Pro-Gun Radio!

description:
Whew, its been a long long time since I edited this. My old description was way out of date. xD

I use OBS to stream to youtube, and because youtube has a terrible chat system that doesn't work in game, I use a telegram group for stream chat stuff, linked in each stream. I'm an angry gamer, who curses out the game a lot, not very excitable like the new age streamers who are very hyperactive and such so don't expect much on that end. I also don't edit my videos that much, especially not streams, because I can't find good software to do so.

If you've come here, you're either a friend, or just browsing around randomly on youtube. Enjoy, fiddle around, whatever. Wait for my next stream so you can hear me cursing everything out every time things don't go my way. :|

description:
The videos presented on the TransAT channel depict the numerical simulations of fluid flows using our CFD software, TransAT.

TransAT (Transport phenomena Analysis Tool) can simulate a wide range of single and multi-fluid/component flows with heat transfer. TransAT is particularly dedicated to predicting fluid-fluid and fluid-solid multiphase flows (CMFD), featuring large density and viscosity ratios. Typical applications range from surface-tension dominated flows (microfluidics) to large-scale turbulent flows.

Contact us at info (AT) ascomp.ch for more information.  

You can also visit us at www.ascomp.ch

「ぼくたちにとって動いて見えるテレビ映像ですら、昆虫から見ればカタカタとした 動きにしか見えない。時間とはいったい何だろうか？」
時間を引きのばして昆虫の世界を見れば、そこには驚異の世界が見えてくる。私たちがスムーズに見えるテレビもカマキリが見たらコマ落としの映像にしかみえないだろう。（なにしろ獲物を捕る速度はわずか1/20秒である）
それほど昆虫の動きは早い。普通のビデオカメラではとらえきれない昆虫の動きや行動を高速度ビデオカメラを用いて時間を10倍から40倍に引き延ばして撮影している。
今では動画はビデオカメラだけでなくスチールカメラでも撮れる。このコーナーでは撮りだめた数々の動画や新しくスチールカメラで撮っている最新動画などを掲載していくことにする。

description: This channel highlights the work of Texas Christian University's Locomotor Performance Lab (LPL).  The LPL specializes in terrestrial locomotion and in relating muscle function to metabolic energy expenditure and performance. Current research focuses on the relationships between the mechanics of movement, performance, metabolic energy expenditure, and metabolic power. This research addresses scientific questions at the whole-body or organism level of biological organization, as well as addressing issues at the tissue and cellular levels.

description:
View supplemental videos from our published reviews. 

Annual Reviews was founded in 1932 as a nonprofit organization dedicated to bringing the most comprehensive scientific review literature to its readers. Annual Reviews journals operate as a high quality filter, prioritizing and synthesizing the primary research literature in 46 different disciplines for the Biomedical, Life, Physical, and Social Sciences, including Economics. All topics for review are selected by an editorial committee comprised of the most distinguished scholars of the discipline. Annual Reviews articles are written by leading scholars to help researchers and students navigate the vast amount of primary research literature that is available to them. As a result, each article is its own search engine, providing a gateway to the most significant literature within a topic.

description:
NASA's mission is to pioneer the future in space exploration, scientific discovery and aeronautics research. To do that, thousands of people have been working around the world and in space for more than 50 years, trying to answer some basic questions. What's out there in space? How do we get there? What will we find? What can we learn there -- or learn just by trying to get there -- that will make life better here on Earth?

NASA's work is diverse: proving flight technologies; creating capabilities for sustainable human and robotic exploration; exploring Earth, the solar system and the universe beyond; developing critical enabling technologies such as the space shuttle; and conducting science in orbit aboard the International Space Station. With NASA you can explore the universe and discover Earth.

description:
This is my channel where I upload gameplay videos of various video games from my computer and gaming consoles.  These variety of videos will randomly span across multiple genres and generations of video games, essentially a video diary of what I have played and how I've progressed.

There will be no background music or commentary, just a pure, unedited gameplay footage in various qualities.  There should be no advertisements in the videos (unless copyright claimed.)  Videos will be published every Monday, Wednesday and Friday (US Eastern Time).

Recordings may include multiplayer games, but the majority of this channel will be focused on the single player experience.  All of these videos are going to be random recordings of games I have played (no requests), either recent, nostalgic and everything in between.  Feel free to browse and search through my video library, who knows what I might have played.  Thank you for watching.

description:
MIKROTRON - a brand of SVS-Vistek GmbH

The MIKROTRON brand is internationally known in the machine vision market for small, particularly robust High-Speed cameras that are used in industrial and scientific applications as well as in sports, advertising and nature filming.

SVS-Vistek GmbH has exceptional know-how in industrial image processing as an innovative manufacturer of high-quality industrial CCD and CMOS cameras for more than 35 years. 
We develop and produce a wide range of standard cameras as well as cameras with the highest resolutions and highest speeds, above-average image quality and all relevant interfaces in our own clean rooms at our headquarters in Gilching near Munich: Quality Made in Germany! 
With subsidiaries in the USA and Japan as well as a large partner network, we can advise, support and serve customers of many markets worldwide.

description:
I'm a female urban explorer who firmly adheres to the explorers' maxim:
 "Take only memories; leave only footprints" - Chief Seattle

With nothing but the utmost respect, I document open abandoned places before they are gone forever, whether through demolition or the act of nature reclaiming what was once hers. If there are no openings in the structures, I do not explore as I do not force entry. I also document ghost towns and historical places of interest. 

For protection of the properties, I do not disclose locations unless they are already well-known.

I hope you join me on my tours!

Honest, concise gadget reviews. I try before you buy!

DISCLOSURES:
I always disclose how I acquired the gadget in the video description. For product samples sent to me directly from manufacturers I disclose that in the video itself. Some products I receive through the Amazon Vine program which are sent to me by Amazon for review on their site. Many other products I buy myself, review, and resell on my store at http://lon.tv/store .

Sometimes I am allowed to keep the products sent to me, but free product never guarantees a positive review. When I receive products I review them. If it's bad I will say so. 

If you'd like for me to review your product, please contact me at lon@lon.tv or send me a note through YouTube. I am happy to send the products back after my review is complete. Channel stats: I currently receive about 1,000,000 views per month.

description: Lake Michigan's fast ferry.  The Milwaukee-based Lake Express ferry began service in 2004, and it is the Midwest's only high-speed auto/passenger ferry. The ferry accommodates 250 passengers, and holds up to 46 vehicles and 12 motorcycles. With terminals in both Milwaukee, Wis. and Muskegon, Mich., Lake Express makes multiple daily trips across Lake Michigan, with each voyage totaling two and one-half hours. Ample parking and easy interstate access are available at both terminals, as well as car rental, taxi and shuttle services. As a fun, fast and easy transportation service, Lake Express has become the premier travel option to avoid lengthy, congested drives through Chicago, Ill. For more information, or to schedule a trip visit www.lake-express.com or call 1-866-914-1010.
